We keep it simple. This privacy policy governs your use of Wordgraphy for iOS that was created by Alper Iskender.
Personal Information
We do not collect any information from our players.
Advertising
Our ads suppliers may use their software development kits (SDK) included in Wordgraphy to personalise ads for you.
You’ll find links to our partners’ privacy policies below:
AdMob:
https://support.google.com/admob/answer/6128543?hl=en&ref_topic=2745287
Chartboost:
https://answers.chartboost.com/en-us/articles/115001489613
Opt-Out Rights
You can always opt-out from settings. On Apple you can opt-out this by choosing ”limit ad tracking” option from privacy settings. On Wordgraphy, you can opt-out this by choosing ”ads tracking” option from the settings.
Your Consent
By using Wordgraphy you accept our Privacy Policy. If you agree with our Privacy Policy, there is nothing you need to do. Please continue to enjoy Wordgraphy.
Links to Other Sites
Wordgraphy may contains our social media page links. If you click on a third-party link, you will be directed to that site. Note that these external sites are not operated by me. Therefore, I strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy of these websites. I have no control over and assume no responsibility for privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our policies, we would be delighted to hear from you by email at
feedback@alperiskender.com